                        <div class="1507752323508 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="cd1f57ce-cbf1-48b9-a280-5bb5bdf60eee" >

    <p><strong>A:</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Take the following actions:<br> </p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Review employee procedures in the&nbsp;<a href="/content/ryerson/policies/policy-list/information-protection-access-policy.html">Information Protection and Access Policy for Restricted Information</a><br> </li> 
 <li>Take Information Security Awareness Training&nbsp;</li> 
 <li>If you are collecting, using, and/or storing other individuals’ personal information (i.e. students or research subjects) 
  <ul> 
   <li>Always use password-protection&nbsp;</li> 
   <li>Password protect your laptop and do not store data on the local drive, use a secure shared drive.</li> 
  </ul> </li> 
 <li>Be extra careful when sharing personal information via email – make sure the address is correct and include only the minimal information necessary to complete the task.</li> 
</ul>
    





