<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="25713745-fc90-416e-8eec-e0d3a5ad8f41" >

    <p><strong>A:</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The same general advice applies with regards to emails with students. Email is not considered a secure or an appropriate vehicle for communicating highly sensitive information.&nbsp; Emails containing personal information that you have used, needs to be retained for a minimum of one year.</p>
    





</div>
