    <p><strong>A:</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The hiring, promotion and tenure review processes are governed by the collective agreement between Ryerson University and the Ryerson Faculty Association. <a href="/hr/collective-agreements/">Collective agreements</a> are accessible under FIPPA and are available for public access.&nbsp; The collective agreement itself provides for certain access to information rights. For more information speak with the Vice Provost, Faculty Affairs.</p>
    





